Classes/KeychainWrapper.html.name: KeychainWrapper
Classes/KeychainWrapper.html.abstract: KeychainWrapper is a class to help make Keychain access in Swift more straightforward. It is designed to make accessing the Keychain services more like using NSUserDefaults, which is much more familiar to people.
